Package: covid19
Title: Download COVID19 Data From The Johns Hopkins COVID19 Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Usman",
           family = "Khaliq",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "usman.khaliq91@gmail.com")
Description: The package provides a day-by-day breakdown of the total number of 
             confirmed, recovered and dead COVID19 cases in each country. 
             Whereever available, the data also includes these figures divided 
             by province/state in specific countries. The source of the data is 
             Johns Hopkins University Centre for Systems Science and Engineering
             (JHU CCSE) Coronavirus.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
